entry.value: SELECT bd.Id, bd.RefId, c.RefId AS ClientRefId, bd.BankRefId, bd.BankAccount, bd.BankAccountType, bd.AccountHolder, bd.BankBranchRefId, bd.CreditCardExiryDate, bd.CardReference, bd.BankingMethod, bd.CardCvv, bd.SecurityNumber, bd.Status, bd.LastActivityDate, bd.ValidationStatus, bd.BankValidationRefId, bd.LastResponseCode FROM customer.ViewClientDetails AS c INNER JOIN dbo.Customers AS cu ON c.AtlasId = cu.UniqueToken INNER JOIN dbo.CurrentCountry() AS country ON cu.CountryRefId = country.RefId INNER JOIN customer.BankingDetails AS bd ON cu.RefId = bd.CustomerRefId and bd.CountryRefId = country.refid

SELECT c.Id, cu.RefId,c.RefId AS ClientRefId , ci.Initials, ci.FirstName, ci.MiddleNames, ci.Surname, ci.LanguageType, ci.GenderType, ci.Title, ci.MaritalStatus, ci.Dependents, ci.Nationality, ci.TypeOfId, ci.PassportNumber, cc.HomeTelephone, cc.WorkTelephone, cc.Fax, 0 AS PostalAddressSameAsPhysical, 0 AS AdvertisingSource, 0 AS AdvertisingContactable, '' AS AdvertisingAnswerDate, cc.WorkEmailAddress, cc.CellContractType, 0 AS HomeOwnerType, 0 AS TimeResided FROM customer.ViewClientDetails AS c INNER JOIN dbo.Customers AS cu ON c.AtlasId = cu.UniqueToken LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.CurrentCountry() AS country ON cu.CountryRefId = country.RefId LEFT OUTER JOIN customer.PersonalDetails AS ci ON cu.RefId = ci.CustomerRefId LEFT OUTER JOIN customer.ContactDetails AS cc ON cu.RefId = cc.CustomerRefId and cc.CountryRefId = country.RefId

SELECT ed.Id, ed.RefId, c.RefId AS ClientRefId, ed.EmployerSectorId, ed.EmploymentLevel, ed.EmploymentType, ed.EmploymentStarted, ed.PaymentFrequency, ed.SalaryRule, ed.SalaryDayRule, ed.PayslipUsername, ed.PayslipPassword, ed.EmployerContactPerson, ed.EmployerContactNumber FROM customer.ViewClientDetails AS c INNER JOIN dbo.Customers AS cu ON c.AtlasId = cu.UniqueToken INNER JOIN dbo.CurrentCountry() AS country ON cu.CountryRefId = country.RefId INNER JOIN customer.EmploymentDetails AS ed ON cu.RefId = ed.CustomerRefId and ed.CountryRefId = country.RefId

SELECT c.Id, cu.RefId,c.RefId AS ClientRefId , ci.Initials, ci.FirstName, ci.MiddleNames, ci.Surname, ci.LanguageType, ci.GenderType, ci.Title, ci.MaritalStatus, ci.Dependents, ci.Nationality, ci.TypeOfId, ci.PassportNumber, cc.HomeTelephone, cc.WorkTelephone, cc.Fax, 0 AS PostalAddressSameAsPhysical, 0 AS AdvertisingSource, 0 AS AdvertisingContactable, '' AS AdvertisingAnswerDate, cc.WorkEmailAddress, cc.CellContractType, 0 AS HomeOwnerType, 0 AS TimeResided FROM customer.ViewClientDetails AS c INNER JOIN dbo.Customers AS cu ON c.AtlasId = cu.UniqueToken LEFT OUTER JOIN dbo.CurrentCountry() AS country ON cu.CountryRefId = country.RefId LEFT OUTER JOIN customer.PersonalDetails AS ci ON cu.RefId = ci.CustomerRefId LEFT OUTER JOIN customer.ContactDetails AS cc ON cu.RefId = cc.CustomerRefId and cc.CountryRefId = country.RefId

select a.Id ID, a.RefId Refid, 0 OwningType, b.REfID OwningRefId, a.AddressType AddressType, left(isnull(a.StreetNumber,'') + ' ' + isnull(a.StreetName,''),250) AddressLine1, left(isnull(a.[Suburb],''),250) AddressLine2, a.City AddressLine3, a.[Province] AddressLine4, convert(nvarchar(50),isnull(a.PostalCode,'')) PostalCode, null AddressNumber, a.[ProvinceLookupKey] ProvinceLookupKey from [customer].[AddressDetails] a inner join customer.CustomerBasicDetails b on a.CustomerRefID = b.CustomerRefID where CountryRefId =2

SELECT ed.Id, ed.RefId, c.RefId AS ClientRefId, ed.EmployerSectorId, ed.EmploymentLevel, ed.EmploymentType, ed.EmploymentStarted, ed.PaymentFrequency, ed.SalaryRule, ed.SalaryDayRule, ed.PayslipUsername, ed.PayslipPassword, ed.EmployerContactPerson, ed.EmployerContactNumber FROM customer.ViewClientDetails AS c INNER JOIN dbo.Customers AS cu ON c.AtlasId = cu.UniqueToken INNER JOIN dbo.CurrentCountry() AS country ON cu.CountryRefId = country.RefId INNER JOIN customer.EmploymentDetails AS ed ON cu.RefId = ed.CustomerRefId and ed.CountryRefId = country.RefId

select a.Id ID, a.RefId Refid, 0 OwningType, b.REfID OwningRefId, a.AddressType AddressType, left(isnull(a.StreetNumber,'') + ' ' + isnull(a.StreetName,''),250) AddressLine1, left(isnull(a.[Suburb],''),250) AddressLine2, a.City AddressLine3, a.[Province] AddressLine4, convert(nvarchar(50),isnull(a.PostalCode,'')) PostalCode, null AddressNumber, a.[ProvinceLookupKey] ProvinceLookupKey from [customer].[AddressDetails] a inner join customer.CustomerBasicDetails b on a.CustomerRefID = b.CustomerRefID where CountryRefId =2

config.comments: select distinct (ac.accountid), case when ac.productid = 21054 then 4 when ac.productid = 21059 then 5 when ac.productid = 21065 then 6 when ac.productid = 21071 then 7 when ac.productid = 21072 then 8 when ac.productid = 21073 then 9 when ac.productid = 21074 then 10 when ac.productid = 21075 then 11 when ac.productid = 21076 then 12 end AS productId, FORMAT(l.ValueDate, 'dd MMMM yyyy') AS submittedOnDate, FORMAT(l.ValueDate, 'dd MMMM yyyy') AS expectedDisbursementDate, l.AccountID + '_' + CAST(l.LoanSeries as nvarchar(4)) AS externalId, CONVERT(DECIMAL(16, 4),li.PrincipalBalance) AS principal, CAST(l.Term as float) AS loanTermFrequency, 2 AS loanTermFrequencyType, CAST(l.Term as float) AS numberOfRepayments, case when l.RepaymentFrequencyID = 'D' then 0 when RepaymentFrequencyID = 'W' then 1 when RepaymentFrequencyID = 'M' then 2 when RepaymentFrequencyID = 'Y' then 3 when RepaymentFrequencyID = 'Q' then 2 end AS repaymentEvery, 2 AS repaymentFrequencyType, CONVERT(DECIMAL(16, 4), l.InterestRate) / 12 AS interestRatePerPeriod, 1 AS interestType, 'false' AS isEqualAmortization, 1 AS amortizationType, 1 AS interestCalculationPeriodType, 'false' AS allowPartialPeriodInterestCalcualtion, 5 AS transactionProcessingStrategyId, ? AS clientId, 'dd MMMM yyyy' AS dateFormat, 'en' AS locale, 'individual' AS loanType, l.LoanStatusID AS LoanStatus, l.ApplicationID AS ApplicationID, ac.ClientID AS brClientId from t_loan (nolock) l left join t_AccountCustomer (nolock) ac on l.accountid = ac.accountid and l.OurBranchID = ac.OurBranchID join t_Product (nolock) p on ac.ProductID = p.ProductID join t_Collateral c (nolock) on c.OwnerClientID = ac.ClientID and c.OurBranchID = l.OurBranchID join t_CollateralVehicle (nolock) cv on cv.CollateralID = c.CollateralID join t_LoanInstallment (nolock) li on li.AccountID = l.AccountID and li.OurBranchID = l.OurBranchID and l.LoanSeries = li.LoanSeries where l.LoanStatusID IN ('A','B','N') and ac.ProductID not in ('LNRP01', 'LSF') and li.InstallmentNo = '1' and li.PrincipalBalance > '1' AND ac.ClientID = ?

AS clientId, 'dd MMMM yyyy' AS dateFormat, 'en' AS locale, 'individual' AS loanType, l.LoanStatusID AS LoanStatus, l.ApplicationID AS ApplicationID, ac.ClientID AS brClientId from t_loan (nolock) l left join t_AccountCustomer (nolock) ac on l.accountid = ac.accountid and l.OurBranchID = ac.OurBranchID join t_Product (nolock) p on ac.ProductID = p.ProductID join t_Collateral c (nolock) on c.OwnerClientID = ac.ClientID and c.OurBranchID = l.OurBranchID join t_CollateralVehicle (nolock) cv on cv.CollateralID = c.CollateralID join t_LoanInstallment (nolock) li on li.AccountID = l.AccountID and li.OurBranchID = l.OurBranchID and l.LoanSeries = li.LoanSeries where l.LoanStatusID IN ('A','B','N') and ac.ProductID not in ('LNRP01', 'LSF') and li.InstallmentNo = '1' and li.PrincipalBalance > '1' AND ac.ClientID = ?

config.comments: SELECT cl.ClientID AS id, SUBSTRING(cl.Name,0,CHARINDEX(' ',cl.Name)) AS firstname, SUBSTRING(cl.Name,CHARINDEX(' ',cl.Name),LEN(cl.Name)) AS lastname, cl.Mobile AS mobileNo, cl.ClientID AS externalId, 1 AS officeId, 1 AS legalFormId, 'false' AS isStaff, 'true' AS active, 'dd MMMM yyyy' AS dateFormat, 'en' AS locale, FORMAT(cl.OpenedDate, 'dd MMMM yyyy') AS activationDate, FORMAT(cl.CreatedOn, 'dd MMMM yyyy') AS submittedOnDate FROM t_Client cl WHERE cl.ClientStatusID = 'A';

entry.value: SELECT distinct (cl.ClientID) AS id, SUBSTRING(cl.Name,0,CHARINDEX(' ',cl.Name)) AS firstname, SUBSTRING(cl.Name,CHARINDEX(' ',cl.Name),LEN(cl.Name)) AS lastname, cl.Mobile AS mobileNo, cl.ClientID AS externalId, 1 AS officeId, 1 AS legalFormId, 'false' AS isStaff, 'true' AS active, 'dd MMMM yyyy' AS dateFormat, 'en' AS locale, FORMAT(cl.OpenedDate, 'dd MMMM yyyy') AS activationDate, FORMAT(cl.OpenedDate, 'dd MMMM yyyy') AS submittedOnDate FROM t_Loan (nolock) l left join t_AccountCustomer (nolock) ac on l.accountid = ac.accountid join t_ClientIndividual (nolock) ci on ci.ClientID = ac.ClientID join t_Client (nolock) cl on cl.ClientID = ci.ClientID WHERE cl.ClientStatusID = 'A' AND l.LoanStatusID NOT IN ('X')

select c.description as make, cv.model as model, cv.ManufactureYear as year_of_manufacture, (ac1.[AccountID] + '_' + CAST(ac1.[AccountSeries] as nvarchar(4))) as Account_number, cv.EngineNo as engine_no, cv.ChassisNo as chasis_no, cv.RegNo as reg_no, cv.marketvalue as market_value, cv.writtendownvalue as forced_value, ? as loan_id from t_collateral (nolock) c left join t_collateralvehicle (nolock) cv on c.collateralid = cv.collateralid join v_AccountCollateral (nolock) ac1 on c.CollateralID = ac1.CollateralID where cv.CollateralDetailStatusID = 'A' and (ac1.[AccountID] + '_' + CAST(ac1.[AccountSeries] as nvarchar(4))) = ?

entry.value: SELECT l.AccountID + '_' + CAST(l.LoanSeries as nvarchar(4)) as accountId, case when cd.ChargeID = 'ADMFEE' then 12 when cd.ChargeID = 'CDLNC1' then 16 when cd.ChargeID = 'CDLNC2' then 47 when cd.ChargeID = 'CDNLC3' then 50 when cd.ChargeID = 'CFTF1' then 66 when cd.ChargeID = 'LGINSCV' then 63 when cd.ChargeID = 'TFN01' then 49 end AS chargeId, c.RecoveryModeID, CONVERT(DECIMAL(16, 4),cd.ChargeAmount/l.Term) AS amount, 'en' AS locale, 'dd MMMM yyyy' AS dateFormat from t_ChargeDue (nolock) cd join t_loan (nolock) l on l.ApplicationID = cd.ApplicationID and l.OurBranchID = cd.OurBranchID join t_Charge (nolock) c on c.ChargeID = cd.ChargeID where c.RecoveryModeID = 'C' and ChargeAmount > '0' and (l.AccountID + '_' + CAST(l.LoanSeries as nvarchar(4))) = ?
